{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c92f1f438f","title":"论考勤制度的缺点","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4b5ce2be9b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c92f1f438f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"25804569a0","name":"蒋兴仁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f01d861cfc","type":"title","text":"论考勤制度的缺点","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"55a98f095b","type":"authors","text":"北京大学蒋兴仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"509a24d650","type":"paragraph","text":"考勤制度是从工厂硬扯过来的，硬套于智力劳动的形式主义的产物。它不但没有鼓舞同学学习积极性，反而限制了同学们的学习的发展。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"82b80c97f9","type":"paragraph","text":"请看—下，它的缺点：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"ced9ecbad0","type":"paragraph","text":"1．只讲究形式上的出勤，不能保证学好与听好。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"74bb18dac1","type":"paragraph","text":"2．由行政指命而作点名汇报的班长，陷于忙乱。并且把同学当作职员，是对同学不尊重。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"116ddaabc4","type":"paragraph","text":"3．强迫同学出勤听课，是对教学质量不高的教师的偏袒与怂恿不能刺激教员提高教学质量，而反使他洋洋自喜，“好不好，反正总有人来听”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"},{"id":"8b993c7607","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f"}],"page":{"id":"d2e3056081","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c92f1f438f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}